= Robotrek (SNES) - Items =

This page documents all items in Robotrek.

== Item Categories ==

* '''Consumables''' - Recovery items, status cures
* '''Equipment''' - Weapons, armor, accessories
* '''Materials''' - Invention components
* '''Key Items''' - Story-related items
* '''Robot Parts''' - Components for building robots

